---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Terms of Use · Blu Baby Show" description="The simple terms for using Blu Baby Show.">
  <section class="section legal">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">Blu Baby Show</p>
      <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
      <p class="muted">Last updated: July 2026</p>

      <p>By using blubabyshow.com you agree to these simple terms.</p>

      <h2>Our content</h2>
      <p>Blu, the characters, videos, artwork, and this site are the property of Blu Baby Show. Please enjoy
        and share our content, but don't copy, resell, or claim it as your own.</p>

      <h2>Purchases</h2>
      <p>Prices and availability may change. Anything you buy is subject to the details shown at checkout,
        including shipping and any return policy stated there.</p>

      <h2>No guarantees</h2>
      <p>Our content is made with love to support families — it isn't medical, psychological, or professional
        advice. Every child is different; trust your instincts and your paediatrician.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hello@blubabyshow.com">hello@blubabyshow.com</a>.</p>

      <p class="muted"><small>This is a plain-language summary and will be expanded before any paid product launches.</small></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .legal { padding-top: calc(var(--nav-h) + 2rem); max-width: 720px; }
  .legal h1 { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .legal h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin-top: 2rem; color: var(--blu-deep); }
  .legal a { color: var(--blu-d); text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
